--Description--
Basic application demonstrating how to create a Spring MVC application with Spring-Data-MongoDB api.

--Functional Aspects--
*A page existing for managing users by CRUD operations
*Used AJAX to avoid page refresh
*Everyone can create new users and edit existing ones
*When editing, users can only edit first name, last name, and role fields
*Made use of Spring-Data-MongoDB interfaces instead manually coding and implementing of data access objects.
